<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Turning Point Diagnostics</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Reset */
        body, table, td, a { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
        table, td { mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }
        img { -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; border: 0; height: auto; line-height: 100%; outline: none; text-decoration: none; }
        body { height: 100% !important; margin: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important; width: 100% !important; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7f6; }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #f4f7f6; margin: 0 !important; padding: 0 !important;">

    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
        <tr>
            <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 10px 40px 10px;">
                
                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
                    
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding: 40px 0 30px 0; border-bottom: 3px solid #0056b3;">
                            <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 28px; color: #0056b3; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: -1px;">
                                Turning Point
                            </h1>
                            <span style="font-size: 14px; color: #666666; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px;">Diagnostics</span>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 40px 30px 40px 30px;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 18px; color: #333333;">
                                Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;">
                                Welcome to Turning Point Diagnostics. We are honored that you have chosen us for your healthcare needs. Your patient profile has been successfully registered in our secure system.
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 30px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;">
                                When your lab results are ready, you will be notified and can access them securely through our patient portal below.
                            </p>

                            <table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
                                <tr>
                                    <td align="center" style="border-radius: 5px;" bgcolor="#0056b3">
                                        <a href="{{link}}" target="_blank" style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px 30px; display: inline-block;">
                                            Access Patient Portal
                                        </a>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                            
                            <p style="margin: 30px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;">
                                If you have any questions before your visit, please do not hesitate to contact our reception desk.
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: #555555;">
                                Sincerely,<br>
                                <strong>The Medical Team</strong>
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="padding: 30px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #999999;">
                                Â© {{currentYear}} Turning Point Diagnostics. All rights reserved.
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #999999;">
                                This is a securely generated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>